gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 122, Trail Blazers 114
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Blazers, 122-114. Collin Sexton led the Jazz with 27 points and four assists as Simone Fontecchio (24 points, 7-8 FG, 5-5 3PT, five rebounds) and Talen Horton-Tucker (23 points) totaled 47 points. Walker Kessler added 10 points, 10 rebounds, and seven blocks for the Jazz. Scoot Henderson totaled his first career double-double with 23 points and 10 assists. The Jazz improve to 9-16 as the Blazers move to 6-17 on the year.
